    public abstract class AbstractLightweightBase40<E extends AbstractLightweightBase40<E>>
extends Object
implements Serializable, Comparable<E>, com.blockwithme.util.shared.AsLong
    AbstractLightweightBase40 represents an abstract base class for 64bit non-negative base-40 values. For a description of the base-40 encoding, see Base40.
